The paper proposes a novel algorithm for improving the stability of prediction in machine learning models when there is model misspecification and agnostic distribution shift. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), statistics (cs.ST), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
